<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<title>Rudrohom Mail</title>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	<style>
		body {
			font-family: 'Poppins' !important;
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<div
		style="max-width: 800px; margin: 15px auto; border: 1px solid #fff; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;border:1px solid #666">
		<div style="padding: 20px 15px; text-align: center;">
			<img src="https://jusbid.in:1337/images/logo_jusbid.png" alt=""
				style="width:200px;height:100%;object-fit: contain;">
		</div>
		<div style="text-align: center">
			<h2 class="wrap_content" style="padding: 0rem 2rem;font-size: 2.2em;color:#000000">Welcome
				<strong>{{name}}</strong>, <br> your account has been approved.
			</h2>
			<h4 class="wrap_content" style="padding: 0rem 2rem;color:#000000">{{createdAt}}</h4>
			<button style="background-color: #25D366;
			color: #ffffff;
			border-radius: 10px;
			border: none;
			padding: 10px 40px;">Welcome to Jusbid Family</button>
		</div>
		<div style="margin:30px 0px;">
			<img style="width:100%" src="{{full_image_path}}">
		</div>
		<div style="padding: 30px 15px; color: #333; font-size: 14px;">
			<div>
				<p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;">
					<strong>{{name}}</strong>,
				</p>
			</div>

			<p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;">
				We are so excited to have you on board. Other employees are looking forward to helping you find your way
				in our company and learn more about what we do here.
				<br><br>
				Your skills will be put to good use as we move on to the next quarter and we canâ€™t wait to see your work
				and show off some of your amazing skills.
				We believe that you will be a great asset to our company. After completion of your on-boarding process
				on DATE, we will introduce you to our policies, culture, and mission. Then you will have a chance to
				meet your supervisor who will inform you all about your new role at our company. Again, congratulations.
				We are thrilled to you have you join the team and look forward to working with you!
				<br><br>
				Please follow steps given below to check your hotelier panel:
				<br>
				1. Click below button or visit <span
					style="font-style: italic;text-decoration: underline;">https://www.jusbid.in/portal/#/partner/hotelier</span><br>
				2. Enter user ID & password generated by system given below (if you are facing issue to find user ID &
				password, please contact support)<br>
				3. By entering your user Id and password, you will see your panel home screen and you can change
				password as needed, keep it safe and strong.<br>
				4. Now you can easily manage your hotel appearance, rooms, bidding, bookings and much more..

			</p>
			<table style="width: 100%">
				<tr>
					<td width="30%">Hotel Name</td>
					<td width="70%"><strong>{{name}}</strong></td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td width="30%">User ID</td>
					<td width="70%"><strong>{{user}}</strong></td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td>Your Password</td>
					<td><strong>{{password}}</strong></td>
				</tr>
			</table>
			<p style="padding: 10px;text-align:center;">
				<a href="https://www.jusbid.in/portal/#/partner/hotelier" target="_blank" style="background-color: #25D366;
					color: #ffffff;
					border-radius: 10px;
					border: none;
					padding: 10px 40px;">
					<span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 16.8px;">Visit Hotelier Panel</span>
				</a>
			</p>
			<p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 10px;">Thank you,</p>
			<p style="font-size: 16px;line-height: 10px;"><strong>Team Rudrohom.</strong></p>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>

</html>